                                <h2>Wash regularly</h2>
                                <p>
                Wash your products regularly to maintain functionality and extend life-cycle. Check out our wash instructions for detailed information. The instructions may varies depends on material.&amp;nbsp;Use every time a washing bag to minimize micro plastic in waste water. &amp;nbsp;</p>
